Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.91,0:02:03.81,OP字幕-2-1,,0000,0000,0000,fx,何度も季节を重ねたね  あの日から{\fad(500,800)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.01,0:02:09.85,OP字幕-2-1,,0000,0000,0000,fx,今日までどうもありがとう{\fad(500,800)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.13,0:02:14.44,OP字幕-2-1,,0000,0000,0000,fx,狭い路地裏目指し{\fad(500,800)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.69,0:02:18.03,OP字幕-2-1,,0000,0000,0000,fx,白い息が踊る{\fad(500,800)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.03,0:02:23.15,OP字幕-2-1,,0000,0000,0000,fx,痛いくらい握った手をひいて{\fad(500,800)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.15,0:02:25.41,OP字幕-2-1,,0000,0000,0000,fx,君は进んでいく{\fad(500,800)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.41,0:02:28.35,OP字幕-2-1,,0000,0000,0000,fx,今すぐキスしたかった{\fad(500,800)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.46,0:02:32.27,OP字幕-2-1,,0000,0000,0000,fx,隠れた自贩机の裏{\fad(500,800)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.47,0:02:35.55,OP字幕-2-1,,0000,0000,0000,fx,はにかんで见つめあった{\fad(500,800)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.77,0:02:40.91,OP字幕-2-1,,0000,0000,0000,fx,优しい気持ちをくれた{\fad(500,800)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.35,0:02:44.55,OP字幕-2-1,,0000,0000,0000,fx,君は君のままで{\fad(500,800)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.94,0:02:48.03,OP字幕-2-1,,0000,0000,0000,fx,僕は僕のままで{\fad(500,800)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.45,0:02:53.39,OP字幕-2-1,,0000,0000,0000,fx,全て分かり合えたなら{\fad(500,800)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.61,0:02:55.63,OP字幕-2-1,,0000,0000,0000,fx,SAY WON 'T STOP LOVE YOU{\fad(500,800)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.63,0:02:58.87,OP字幕-2-1,,0000,0000,0000,fx,どんな小さな幸せも{\fad(500,800)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.12,0:03:02.44,OP字幕-2-1,,0000,0000,0000,fx,见つけ出せる気がするよ{\fad(500,800)}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.49,0:03:08.04,OP字幕-2-1,,0000,0000,0000,fx,优しくなれたのは  君のおかげ{\fad(500,800)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.68,0:01:46.11,OP字幕-2-2,,0000,0000,0000,fx,原本的你{\fad(500,800)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.25,0:01:49.33,OP字幕-2-2,,0000,0000,0000,fx,原本的我{\fad(500,800)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.33,0:01:55.20,OP字幕-2-2,,0000,0000,0000,fx,若能彼此理解{\fad(500,800)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.91,0:02:03.81,OP字幕-2-2,,0000,0000,0000,fx,自四季轮回交替之日{\fad(500,800)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.01,0:02:09.85,OP字幕-2-2,,0000,0000,0000,fx,谢谢你至今陪伴着我{\fad(500,800)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.13,0:02:14.44,OP字幕-2-2,,0000,0000,0000,fx,朝着狭窄的角落{\fad(500,800)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.69,0:02:18.03,OP字幕-2-2,,0000,0000,0000,fx,呼出白色的气息{\fad(500,800)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.03,0:02:23.15,OP字幕-2-2,,0000,0000,0000,fx,使劲地拉着我的手{\fad(500,800)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.15,0:02:25.41,OP字幕-2-2,,0000,0000,0000,fx,你带着我不断前进{\fad(500,800)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.41,0:02:28.35,OP字幕-2-2,,0000,0000,0000,fx,想要立刻亲吻你{\fad(500,800)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.46,0:02:32.27,OP字幕-2-2,,0000,0000,0000,fx,藏在自动售货机背后{\fad(500,800)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.47,0:02:35.55,OP字幕-2-2,,0000,0000,0000,fx,害羞地凝望对方{\fad(500,800)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.77,0:02:40.91,OP字幕-2-2,,0000,0000,0000,fx,温暖的气息充满心中{\fad(500,800)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.35,0:02:44.55,OP字幕-2-2,,0000,0000,0000,fx,你还是原来的你{\fad(500,800)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.94,0:02:48.03,OP字幕-2-2,,0000,0000,0000,fx,我也是原来的我{\fad(500,800)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.45,0:02:53.39,OP字幕-2-2,,0000,0000,0000,fx,若能彼此理解{\fad(500,800)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.61,0:02:55.63,OP字幕-2-2,,0000,0000,0000,fx,说 不会停止对你的爱{\fad(500,800)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.63,0:02:58.87,OP字幕-2-2,,0000,0000,0000,fx,再小幸福{\fad(500,800)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.12,0:03:02.44,OP字幕-2-2,,0000,0000,0000,fx,似乎也能握在手中{\fad(500,800)}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.49,0:03:08.04,OP字幕-2-2,,0000,0000,0000,fx,我能变得如此温柔  全因为是你{\fad(500,800)}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.31,0:22:15.10,ED歌词-3-2,,0000,0000,0000,,心里紧紧的 只有一点点哦{\fad(500,800)}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.10,0:22:18.50,ED歌词-3-1,,0000,0000,0000,,若这样被你牵绊住{\fad(500,800)}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.50,0:22:23.04,ED歌词-3-1,,0000,0000,0000,,是否就是真正的爱恋呢{\fad(500,800)}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.54,0:22:33.59,ED歌词-3-1,,0000,0000,0000,,在光鲜的草坪上  嬉戏打滚{\fad(500,800)}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.66,0:22:39.19,ED歌词-3-1,,0000,0000,0000,,纯真无邪的幼年时光{\fad(500,800)}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.37,0:22:45.24,ED歌词-3-1,,0000,0000,0000,,但从心中孕育的感情{\fad(500,800)}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.24,0:22:49.98,ED歌词-3-1,,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢开始萌芽{\fad(500,800)}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.64,0:22:57.05,ED歌词-3-1,,0000,0000,0000,,总是与你共度相同的时间{\fad(500,800)}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.30,0:23:03.72,ED歌词-3-1,,0000,0000,0000,,却只是远远徘徊 无法坦诚我的内心{\fad(500,800)}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.91,0:23:11.81,ED歌词-3-1,,0000,0000,0000,,心里紧紧的 在你身旁却是安静的{\fad(500,800)}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.86,0:23:18.16,ED歌词-3-1,,0000,0000,0000,,抱住你 凝视着你{\fad(500,800)}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.58,0:23:23.41,ED歌词-3-1,,0000,0000,0000,,这是小小的爱恋的开始{\fad(500,800)}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.51,0:23:31.50,ED歌词-3-1,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然现在仍难以表白 我喜欢你{\fad(500,800)}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.24,0:22:15.10,ED歌词-3-1,,0000,0000,0000,,心がきゅんと 少しだけきゅんと{\fad(500,800)}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.10,0:22:18.50,ED歌词-3-2,,0000,0000,0000,,しめつけられたなら{\fad(500,800)}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.50,0:22:23.04,ED歌词-3-2,,0000,0000,0000,,本当の恋 なのかな...{\fad(500,800)}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.54,0:22:33.59,ED歌词-3-2,,0000,0000,0000,,光る芝生の上 ふざけて寝転んだね{\fad(500,800)}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.66,0:22:39.19,ED歌词-3-2,,0000,0000,0000,,無邪気だった 幼かった日々{\fad(500,800)}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.37,0:22:45.24,ED歌词-3-2,,0000,0000,0000,,でも心の奥で育ってゆく感情{\fad(500,800)}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.24,0:22:49.98,ED歌词-3-2,,0000,0000,0000,,少しずつ気づき始めてた{\fad(500,800)}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.64,0:22:57.05,ED歌词-3-2,,0000,0000,0000,,同じ時間を過ごした分だけ{\fad(500,800)}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.30,0:23:03.72,ED歌词-3-2,,0000,0000,0000,,素直になれなくて遠回りした{\fad(500,800)}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.91,0:23:11.81,ED歌词-3-2,,0000,0000,0000,,心でぎゅっと　隣でそっと{\fad(500,800)}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.86,0:23:18.16,ED歌词-3-2,,0000,0000,0000,,抱きしめてあなたを見つめてるよ{\fad(500,800)}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.58,0:23:23.41,ED歌词-3-2,,0000,0000,0000,,それは小さな恋の始まり{\fad(500,800)}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.51,0:23:31.50,ED歌词-3-2,,0000,0000,0000,,今はまだ言えないけど あなたがスキ...だよ{\fad(500,800)}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.84,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.82,0:00:05.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 注意不要受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.81,0:00:09.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵循实行委员的指示把东西收拾好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.51,0:00:10.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.82,0:00:13.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,创立祭终于顺利结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.72,0:00:20.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年的关东煮保持了游泳部传统的味道而大受好评
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.93,0:00:21.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松一口气了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.15,0:00:22.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.18,0:00:28.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七咲我打算把这秘方托付给你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.27,0:00:27.91,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（关东煮摊档秘方 秘传）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.95,0:00:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是交给二年级的前辈而是交给我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.80,0:00:35.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我希望你能接受
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.04,0:00:38.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做的萝卜味道很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.88,0:00:41.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会 比不上学姐做的海带
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.11,0:00:45.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七咲 你要继承这秘方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.54,0:00:49.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后继续将游泳部传统的味道保持下去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.19,0:00:54.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.04,0:01:03.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小逢 明年拜托你做多一点我喜欢的鱼糕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.80,0:01:05.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会满怀期待地跟响来品尝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.98,0:01:08.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到时不知道会不会来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.84,0:01:12.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会 来吃鱼糕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.59,0:01:17.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梨穗 你那边好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.92,0:01:20.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 差不多收拾好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.65,0:01:21.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.53,0:01:25.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年要结束了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.62,0:01:26.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.12,0:01:29.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是光阴似箭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.22,0:01:33.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是那样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.33,0:01:35.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.78,0:01:37.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟着我来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.37,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.35,0:03:19.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.45,0:03:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯一为什么在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.72,0:03:24.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么吗 是学姐叫我来的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.46,0:03:27.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为答谢他之前的帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.17,0:03:37.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在青空下品茶 感觉不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.36,0:03:40.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真高雅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.54,0:03:42.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是啊是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.15,0:03:48.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,领略高雅 其路坎坷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.97,0:03:53.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 比起夏天在烈日下好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.64,0:03:58.85,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1050,500)\fad(150,150)}樱井梨穗子篇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.64,0:03:58.85,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1050,540)\fad(150,150)}第三章
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.64,0:03:58.85,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1050,600)\fad(150,150)}继承
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.38,0:03:58.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 费那么多功夫到外面品茶不觉得另有一番情趣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.85,0:04:05.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,体会情趣 前路坎坷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.34,0:04:07.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许真的是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.41,0:04:13.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然被炉就是天堂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.20,0:04:16.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梨穗 小心在被炉里睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.42,0:04:20.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔会有露天茶筵的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.68,0:04:24.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在早春时为了招新会举办一次
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.86,0:04:27.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.74,0:04:30.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为很普通 新生都不太关注
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.28,0:04:33.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且去年以为下雨的关系而中止了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.27,0:04:36.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精心准备好的点心都浪费了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.27,0:04:39.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真是令人头疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.20,0:04:45.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 幸亏有那唯一的新部员帮我们处理得一干二净
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.56,0:04:47.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.56,0:04:51.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.27,0:05:00.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得露天茶筵挺不错的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.55,0:05:01.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.82,0:05:05.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外能放上音乐就更好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.47,0:05:09.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这又不符合感受自然的理念
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.22,0:05:12.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音乐…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.32,0:05:16.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音乐吗 你的意见不错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.14,0:05:18.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.25,0:05:21.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明年那样做的话也许不错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.92,0:05:22.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好提议
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.87,0:05:27.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邀请吹奏乐部一同举办
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.54,0:05:29.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.39,0:05:30.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了 小梨穗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.17,0:05:33.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们明年会来看的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.96,0:05:34.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.40,0:05:39.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 明年春天学姐们毕业了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.63,0:05:40.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.85,0:05:42.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里会变冷清
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.75,0:05:43.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.44,0:05:46.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会保护茶道部的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.01,0:05:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来把东西收拾一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.04,0:05:55.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦呀 对茶有兴趣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.68,0:06:02.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 做起来原来这么难
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.85,0:06:03.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.58,0:06:06.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茶道是深奥的学问
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.97,0:06:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊 做不好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.58,0:06:12.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.59,0:06:15.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯一 要换我帮你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.35,0:06:17.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.20,0:06:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉跟学姐们完全不同
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.20,0:06:25.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨穗子跟我差别不大吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.20,0:06:28.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.15,0:06:33.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 学姐们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.48,0:06:34.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.77,0:06:35.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.58,0:06:37.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.06,0:06:39.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心别摔倒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.74,0:06:41.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 再见…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.42,0:06:44.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好重…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.81,0:06:46.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.28,0:06:51.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才说完不久小梨穗就回应了我们的期待了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.81,0:06:56.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明年也请多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.14,0:06:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对、对不起啊 纯一
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.18,0:07:05.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊 梨穗子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.47,0:07:08.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收拾工作真是辛苦你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.31,0:07:14.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茶道部的茶会十分成功啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.69,0:07:15.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢赞赏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.91,0:07:18.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天给你们添麻烦了 真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.96,0:07:23.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝甜米酒会醉成那样子的恐怕只有老师你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.04,0:07:25.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真丢人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.92,0:07:28.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师 明年要注意哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.13,0:07:30.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吸取教训
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.38,0:07:32.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会注意的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.63,0:07:36.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实行委员真能干啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.53,0:07:39.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为梨穗子我们得讨好她
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.58,0:07:41.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便拍拍马屁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.58,0:07:45.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.46,0:07:48.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然已经25号了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.44,0:07:52.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但能凑齐三个人开庆祝会真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.35,0:07:53.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.73,0:07:56.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟美也连续庆祝两天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.08,0:08:00.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你们为我做那么多
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.64,0:08:04.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这蛋糕和这些料理是中多同学带来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.04,0:08:08.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 一说今天要在美也家庆祝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.18,0:08:13.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸就做好这些叫我拿过来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.30,0:08:14.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很厉害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.42,0:08:17.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很大的蛋糕 能吃得完吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.15,0:08:19.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.48,0:08:21.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于蛋糕我有两个胃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.43,0:08:25.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我昨天收到两位的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.26,0:08:28.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我要给两人回礼 给
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.32,0:08:31.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.39,0:08:35.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 纯一
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.05,0:08:37.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天有时间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.06,0:08:40.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.03,0:08:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算说在减肥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.33,0:08:48.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一味让我点吃的 你却只喝水也不好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.15,0:08:50.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨穗子也要些吃的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.65,0:08:55.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为人家刚才在活动室已经吃了很多点心了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.39,0:08:58.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不节制一下的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.40,0:09:07.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 你用那种眼神看着我叫我怎样吃下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.59,0:09:10.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你吃一半吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.40,0:09:14.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不行 我会忍耐的了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.54,0:09:17.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话就别用那种眼神看着蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.91,0:09:19.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.83,0:09:22.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖啡要续杯吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.89,0:09:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 薰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.94,0:09:27.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞节也要打工啊 真辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.64,0:09:28.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还过得去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.88,0:09:32.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过相反的 在除夕和元旦能够休息
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.08,0:09:36.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每年31日和妈妈一起大扫除
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.08,0:09:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备新年料理 然后中午12点去初诣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.57,0:09:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.55,0:09:48.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 那么请慢用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.80,0:09:52.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 你要对我说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.52,0:09:55.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…纯一
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.00,0:09:59.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于之前礼物的回礼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.28,0:10:02.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 想到要什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.73,0:10:03.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.75,0:10:06.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…就是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.86,0:10:10.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想一起去初诣之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.85,0:10:13.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.80,0:10:14.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.66,0:10:17.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 不过这样就可以了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.57,0:10:22.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么31日夜晚到我家来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.57,0:10:25.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 还是把蛋糕给我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.33,0:10:27.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 随便
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.86,0:10:35.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.62,0:10:37.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是香苗同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.03,0:10:40.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香苗? 在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.57,0:10:41.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.19,0:10:46.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果香苗同学看到减肥中的梨穗子竟然在吃蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.03,0:10:48.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该会很生气吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.25,0:10:50.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里 哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.36,0:10:51.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 就在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.90,0:10:54.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.13,0:10:56.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗你的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.19,0:11:01.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌 纯一总是在说谎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.86,0:11:10.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 梨穗子 你干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.16,0:11:15.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前叫我帮忙减肥的不是梨穗子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.62,0:11:18.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 是这样没错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.73,0:11:22.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天吃下去的份量在之后的运动中消耗掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.28,0:11:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会比平常做更多的运动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.58,0:11:29.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题 没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.11,0:11:41.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电话 电话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.84,0:11:44.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥 接电话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.52,0:11:47.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快来接电话啊 老哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.56,0:11:49.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 我现在下来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.19,0:11:54.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美也 你那样子是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.86,0:11:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还没洗完澡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.55,0:12:00.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很冷啊 你快点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.99,0:12:02.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁打来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.14,0:12:03.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梅原
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.35,0:12:05.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.81,0:12:14.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊 美少女为了接我的电话特意从浴室里走出来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.66,0:12:16.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还穿着浴巾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.39,0:12:16.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我挂了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.12,0:12:18.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 等等 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.16,0:12:22.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寒假时一起去买之前说过的那张新影碟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.91,0:12:24.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以啊 什么时候去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.24,0:12:26.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除夕那天去怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.33,0:12:32.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不在之后直接到大将家举行鉴赏会如何
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.93,0:12:35.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,题材由你选择
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.61,0:12:40.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 还有让我玩玩之前那个新射击游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.48,0:12:42.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 除夕不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.16,0:12:45.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要跟梨穗子一起去初诣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.97,0:12:48.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 你这叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.24,0:12:49.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么叛徒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.66,0:12:52.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好意思说 竟然跟樱井同学去初诣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.82,0:12:55.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在什么时候发展到那种关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.82,0:12:58.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真过分 竟然一直瞒着我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.38,0:12:59.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真冷淡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.54,0:13:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我说多少遍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.23,0:13:04.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨穗子只是青梅竹马
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.65,0:13:06.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大将 你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.55,0:13:09.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樱井同学有着很高的人气
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.49,0:13:11.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有男生给她送过情书
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.40,0:13:13.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.34,0:13:18.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸福也许就近在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.51,0:13:23.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚才很有诗人的风范吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.91,0:13:26.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样 不错的名言吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.67,0:13:28.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是  啊对了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.07,0:13:30.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要来的话就今天来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.32,0:13:33.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有东西要跟你借
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.62,0:13:37.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约到他了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.96,0:13:39.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得不错啊 樱井
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.01,0:13:40.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.95,0:13:45.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 虽然很好 但也有个很遗憾的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.02,0:13:47.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.36,0:13:50.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我今天把一个很甜的蛋糕…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.04,0:13:52.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你吃掉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.52,0:13:56.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 纯一说要给我吃于是就…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.52,0:13:58.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.70,0:14:01.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我会好好运动的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.48,0:14:03.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把吃下去的消耗掉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.62,0:14:06.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 加油吧 樱井
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.99,0:14:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2…3…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.84,0:14:20.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明目标是…一百次 不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.01,0:14:23.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟纯一一起去初诣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.22,0:14:26.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好期待
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.97,0:14:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 美也 去开门吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.13,0:14:36.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美也 你不在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.74,0:14:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么去了 没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.26,0:14:42.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了 来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.19,0:14:44.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 美也
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.40,0:14:47.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 原来是梨穗子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.06,0:14:47.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.52,0:14:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.98,0:14:55.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯一你真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.57,0:14:59.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来得真早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.64,0:15:03.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 想早来跟美也聚聚旧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.83,0:15:07.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘻嘻嘻 一起去吃除夕荞麦面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.92,0:15:08.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.89,0:15:11.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 差不多可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.89,0:15:18.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.79,0:15:19.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.34,0:15:24.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近老哥经常泡茶喝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.53,0:15:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前都没这样做的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.84,0:15:31.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我向学姐们请教泡茶的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.64,0:15:32.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就迷下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.79,0:15:38.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯一泡的也许比我的还好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.99,0:15:43.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,热水的温度和蒸煮时间很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.25,0:15:45.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是美味的秘诀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.09,0:15:47.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你神气个鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.81,0:15:48.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么问题
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.83,0:15:52.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 好 两位别为了点小事吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.91,0:15:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 吃这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.85,0:15:56.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我挑战做的新款式
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.31,0:15:58.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶酪蛋奶酥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.26,0:16:02.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 很好吃的样子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.75,0:16:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶酪蛋奶酥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.63,0:16:07.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,减肥怎么样了 梨穗子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.29,0:16:12.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做这些奶酪蛋奶酥时候我控制的砂糖的份量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.49,0:16:15.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得奶酪的卡路里很高
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.00,0:16:18.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.77,0:16:20.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.12,0:16:24.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真的啊 这个很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.43,0:16:26.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.78,0:16:28.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.04,0:16:33.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多到令人期待的节目了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.65,0:16:37.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年的压轴演员是谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.76,0:16:39.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是小三太
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.36,0:16:41.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.69,0:16:43.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.45,0:16:47.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样说的话 今年那个偶像组合应该会登场
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.47,0:16:49.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好期待啊 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.05,0:16:52.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美也也喜欢这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.73,0:16:53.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.07,0:17:22.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 梨穗很有型啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.55,0:17:24.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 很不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.20,0:17:25.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.29,0:17:30.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘻嘻嘻 这样以来我们俩能登台表演了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.41,0:17:33.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,登台就有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.27,0:17:34.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.66,0:17:37.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢唱歌 但成为偶像有点那个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.05,0:17:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.39,0:17:41.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没有什么原因
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.48,0:17:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.70,0:17:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥 把电视机的遥控器给我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.04,0:17:49.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在你那边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.10,0:17:51.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.71,0:17:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为成为了偶像一定不能像这样过除夕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.20,0:18:00.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 差不多该走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.35,0:18:04.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 不过美也睡着了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.91,0:18:06.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.75,0:18:10.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去准备一下 梨穗子能帮我叫醒美也吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.97,0:18:13.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.80,0:18:15.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美也 美也
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.12,0:18:22.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 准备妥当 啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.39,0:18:26.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 准备妥当
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.47,0:18:32.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.94,0:18:35.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么叫人起来却连自己都睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.59,0:18:41.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实黄豆年糕也不错 还有花生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.54,0:18:44.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连梦也是那么奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.41,0:19:00.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樱井现在应该跟橘在一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.36,0:19:11.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.98,0:19:15.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初诣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.50,0:19:19.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯一 美也 快起来 我们睡过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.40,0:19:25.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人不多真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.68,0:19:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.01,0:19:31.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在新一天前后来的话至少要排一小时的队
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.42,0:19:33.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.84,0:19:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 高考前我也跟纯一来过这里祈求合格
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.21,0:19:49.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨穗子总是在做数学题的时候睡着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.73,0:19:53.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨穗子 做出答案了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.49,0:20:10.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 在暑假的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.01,0:20:13.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.62,0:20:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.17,0:20:20.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.13,0:20:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后总是在分神
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.07,0:20:31.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后只是一味吃东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.51,0:20:37.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 总算能够合格
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.33,0:20:46.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.12,0:20:47.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.21,0:20:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼物的回礼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.20,0:20:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.46,0:20:54.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写上你的愿望 然后挂到那里去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.03,0:20:59.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写什么好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.64,0:21:02.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没想好写什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.05,0:21:04.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.61,0:21:07.98,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（愿减肥能成功）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.61,0:21:07.98,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（愿茶道部有新部员加入）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.15,0:21:08.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥 梨穗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.19,0:21:10.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们去求签吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.68,0:21:14.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.16,0:21:24.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 我是大吉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.00,0:21:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小吉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.15,0:21:28.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是末吉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.50,0:21:29.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.24,0:21:33.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,末吉跟小吉哪一个更幸运呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.62,0:21:36.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“末”从字面上看就是最后的意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.90,0:21:40.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是「末广がり」的「末」应该有很好的运势
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.90,0:21:40.81,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（末广がり：逐渐繁荣昌盛的意思）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.90,0:21:42.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘻嘻嘻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.75,0:21:46.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快退下 大吉的本小姐要通过
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.00,0:21:48.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.42,0:21:49.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 有红豆汤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.18,0:21:51.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.68,0:21:52.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红豆汤吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.68,0:21:55.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在新年吃一下也无妨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.83,0:21:57.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么 纯一
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.48,0:21:59.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨穗子吃没年糕的红豆汤
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.19,0:22:04.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那算不上是红豆汤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.14,0:22:08.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（我的心意能传达给他）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.90,0:23:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集预告
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.50,0:23:44.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于又过了一年看 小梨穗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.79,0:23:45.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新年快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.81,0:23:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年也请多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.04,0:23:49.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 今年也…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.92,0:23:52.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 今年我们都毕业了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.39,0:23:53.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.99,0:23:54.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糊涂虫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.10,0:23:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我好好干啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.25,0:23:57.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.17,0:23:58.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告别
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.48,0:24:01.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要尽快找到新部员
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.86,0:24:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到的只是新部员吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.96,0:24:06.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱~人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.72,0:24:07.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,

